### PathAI Phase 2 - REST API Examples
### Copy these cURL commands or use in Postman/Thunder Client

## Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = <your_jwt_token_from_login>

---

## 1. SIGNUP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Abhay Sharma",
  "email": "abhay@learningpath.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "learningGoal": "Master React and TypeScript"
}

### Response:
{
  "message": "User registered successfully",
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "user": {
    "id": "65abc123def456...",
    "name": "Abhay Sharma",
    "email": "abhay@learningpath.com"
  }
}

---

## 2. LOGIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "abhay@learningpath.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

---

## 3. GET CURRENT USER PROFILE
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

## 4. UPDATE PROFILE
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "learningGoal": "Advanced React + Node.js",
  "learningStyle": "visual"
}

---

## 5. GENERATE ROADMAP (via n8n proxy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/n8n/generate-roadmap
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

