## TESTING WORKFLOW

### Session Flow (Complete User Journey)
1. POST /auth/signup → Get token
2. POST /n8n/generate-roadmap → Create roadmap
3. GET /roadmaps → See all roadmaps
4. POST /streak/checkin → Daily check-in
5. POST /quiz/generate → Start quiz
6. POST /quiz/submit → Submit answers
7. GET /auth/me → See updated profile (XP, level, badges)

---

## POSTMAN COLLECTION SETUP

Import this as a Postman environment:
```json
{
  "name": "PathAI Phase 2",
  "values": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000/api",
      "enabled": true
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}
```

After signup, copy the token into the `token` variable.

